questions: What is the start date of medication with the code {medication_code}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX ct:<https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#umls:RxNorm> SELECT ?start WHERE {{ ?medication a syn:Medication; syn:code '{medication_code}'^^ct:; syn:startDateTime ?start.}}
